gov.nih.nlm.meme.beans
Class ClientBean

java.lang.Object
  gov.nih.nlm.meme.beans.ClientBean
Direct Known Subclasses:
ActionDetailsBean, ActionHarvesterBean, ActionSequenceBean, AdminClientBean, AuxiliaryDataClientBean, ContentViewBean, MappingBean, ReleaseBean, TestSuiteSetBean, WorklistLookupBean
public abstract class ClientBean
extends Object

Parent of all other beans, tracks "host", "port", and "mid service" parameters. Supports the "configureClient" method used by subclasses to configure MEME Client API classes with these three parameters.

Author:
MEME Group

configureClient

public void configureClient(ClientAPI client)
Configures client by setting host and port parameters. Not all clients make use of a "mid service" so those that do must override this method to also set that parameter.

Parameters:
client - the MEME ClientAPI to configure
